nl.esciencecenter.xenon.adaptors.scripting

Class ScriptingAdaptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.esciencecenter.xenon.engine.Adaptor
      • nl.esciencecenter.xenon.adaptors.scripting.ScriptingAdaptor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GridEngineAdaptor, SlurmAdaptor, TorqueAdaptor

    public abstract class ScriptingAdaptor
extends Adaptor
    ScriptingAdaptor is a generic adaptor implementation. It server as a parent class for adaptors that are based on running scripts over an SSH connection.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    GridEngineAdaptor, SlurmAdaptor
